"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且我地日日遊行，係外國人眼中好悶㗎。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">要有多啲gimmick佢地先會重新關注</span></span>。<br />\n時間、地點我唔知應該點定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但如果真係搞面具人鏈，我地可以帶上自製嘅四川面譜、facepainting、動物面膜、超人、Mario、多啦A夢、V煞⋯⋯冇嘅話純戴口罩都得，不過口罩上可以畫野。總之約精彩越好玩越好<br />\n我地<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">依家好需要一個嘉年華式抗爭</span></span>去緩和下大家嘅情緒，同獲得國際認同。好似之前雷射革命咁。<br />\n<br />\n如果各位手足覺得呢個建議ok，就開多另一個po去講時間地點啦。<br />\n（大家都要考慮一個問題就係，面具人鏈會唔會被狗拉，如果會嘅話⋯⋯都係諗諗先。畢竟expect一家大細出席，怕會全家被告）<br />\n<br />\np牌求推"},{"pid":"170bf6b46b5385ccf1a14ac15faffdc423a8ee5d","tid":1632650,"uid":266741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1e7e1194b9491db0bd2fd162153c9a62ed99b28","tid":1632650,"uid":201464,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"23f650523ff2eb78db47eb48c72f0fc5a6ee42f9","tid":1632650,"uid":121095,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"a251d350fa70c67616de4b655dd576cbb23fd373","tid":1632650,"uid":201464,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:31:18.000Z","msg":"馬上風#121095：我宣布，前線即日起要私了埋記者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1632160/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1632160/page/1</a><br />\n書面與達人#77788<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/profile/77788\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/profile/77788</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:43:19.000Z","msg":"你老母就親中<br />\n睇完都唔明想講咩既話<br />\n我好擔心大家個心態"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:51:17.000Z","msg":"做乜咁驚？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇人會無啦啦話私了埋記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:03:47.000Z","msg":"黑狗偷左義士手機玩帶風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55c55f46e358c836f0ae18f05f710159277dd158","tid":1632650,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0